snippet.title: Tailwinds // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://metalharbor.itch.io/tailwinds

Welcome to Tailwinds, a Pilotwings-inspired mod for Sonic Robo Blast 2, 
featuring a story loosely based on the little-known Chuck Yeager origin story.
Play through 26 missions in this 1-2 hour game.

SRB2 is distributed with permission from Sonic Team Junior.

Developed by Metal Harbor
